{"tid":1784783,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「沙甸魚運動」 逼爆意大利羅馬反法西斯","createTime":"2019-12-16T02:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T07:43:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8aafdc412eb1b7982fc24fb60dc610407d802f2f","tid":1784783,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:36:29.000Z","msg":"意大利近期出現名為「沙甸魚」(the sardines)的示威，數萬名包括學生、退休人士甚至兒童的民眾，前日逼爆意大利羅馬聖若望廣場(Piazza San Giovanni)，抗議當地極右勢力坐大，矛頭指向前內政部長薩爾維尼(Matteo Salvini)領導的右翼聯盟黨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9L7UGN4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9L7UGN4.jpg&h=75e0105a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「沙甸魚運動」始於上月，由32歲的桑托里(Mattia Santori)及3位朋友在北部城巿博洛尼亞發起，示威其後蔓延多個城市。桑托里稱沙甸魚代表以意念填滿空間或對抗敵人，指運動已由反對聯盟黨，擴展為反法西斯、支持平等，反對不寬容、反對排外和反對歧視同性戀者等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%8c%e6%b2%99%e7%94%b8%e9%ad%9a%e3%80%8d%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81-%e9%80%bc%e7%88%86%e7%be%85%e9%a6%ac%e5%8f%8d%e5%8f%b3%e7%bf%bc-200324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%25b2%2599%25e7%2594%25b8%25e9%25ad%259a%25e3%2580%258d%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581-%25e9%2580%25bc%25e7%2588%2586%25e7%25be%2585%25e9%25a6%25ac%25e5%258f%258d%25e5%258f%25b3%25e7%25bf%25bc-200324&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hgomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=e7bfc1b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%8c%e6%b2%99%e7%94%b8%e9%ad%9a%e3%80%8d%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81-%e9%80%bc%e7%88%86%e7%be%85%e9%a6%ac%e5%8f%8d%e5%8f%b3%e7%bf%bc-200324</a>"},{"pid":"0612b4a8e5eac02c022091bcfd7f8598de6a4ec9","tid":1784783,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:43:59.000Z","msg":"全球抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}